overview: It's that time of the semester again that all college students fear - midterms. Poor Kelly and the girls of PiPi house don't have a prayer. How in the world will they ever pass their test? They were so busy all semester with the parties and social events and fucking and sucking they just didn't have time to crack a book. Crack an ass? Yes. But book? C'mon, they're young, dumb and full of cum. But now it's time to make the grade and these girls are nothing but resourceful.
title: Kelly the Coed 16
